oman, times, serif\">　　Aiming to provide high-quality education to our students, GCU ranks the 7th among top 300 independent colleges in China by CUAA.net in 2017 and enjoys the reputation of &ldquo;Five-Star College&rdquo;, &ldquo;First-rate Independent College&rdquo; and &ldquo;China&rsquo;s Most Competitive College in Job Market&rdquo;.<br />\r\n　　GCU values educational internationalization and has established collaborations with universities from USA, UK, Canada, Australia, the Netherlands, France, etc. Every year hundreds of students participate in the various cross-cultural exchanges, or international cooperation programs to study abroad. There are international students from west Europe and South-east Asia studying at GCU, creating a multi-cultural and diverse atmosphere.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman, times, serif\"><strong>II. Academic Programs</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width: 583px\" width=\"563\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n	<tr>\r\n	<td nowrap=\"nowrap\" style=\"width: 161px; height: 22px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman, times, serif\"><strong>Academic Schools</strong></span></span></td>\r\n	<td nowrap=\"nowrap\" style=\"width: 402px; height: 22px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman, times, serif\"><strong>Undergraduate Programs</strong></span></span></td>\r\n	<td height=\"22\" style=\"height: 22px\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n	<td nowrap=\"nowrap\" rowspan=\"4\" style=\"width: 161px; height: 22px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman, times, serif\">International Business School</span></span></td>\r\n	<td nowrap=\"nowrap\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 402px; height: 22px\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family: times new roman, times, serif\">Int